itz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mark Spitz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Spitz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Spitz\"}, {\"begin\": 693, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carl Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carl_Lewis\"}, {\"begin\": 720, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larisa Latynina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\"}, {\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"score\": 0.9993920739762999, \"rank\": 0.0005883572268353045, \"text\": \"Finnish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland\"}, {\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paavo_Nurmi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paavo Nurmi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paavo_Nurmi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paavo_Nurmi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nine total gold medals\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 635}, {\"ngram\": \"Ledecky\", \"from\": 637, \"to\": 644}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic history\", \"from\": 786, \"to\": 801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only Phelps, who claimed 23 Olympic golds in his legendary career, owns more.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 881, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 809, \"end\": 815, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/William_H._Phelps_Sr.\", \"score\": 0.9999999989361186, \"rank\": 1.061