655, \"to\": 1663}, {\"ngram\": \"her legacy\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"home soil\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd love to (compete in 2028), but it's not easy,\\\" Ledeckysaid.\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1798, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\" Ledeckysaid\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1797}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will take it year by year, and give it everything I have got for as long as I have left in me.\\\"\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"year\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1827}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1851}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Associated Press contributed to this story.\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1903, \"end\": 1919, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9786335233842899, \"rank\": 0.02183285566261616, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this story\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1945}]}]}"